        <paragraph id="par_id3835261" role="paragraph">Choose <menuitem>Format - Object - Line</menuitem> (Calc).</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="par_id3148668" role="paragraph">On <emph>Line and Filling</emph> bar, click</paragraph>
